# CoachPro - Sports Coaching Management App

A full-featured Android app for managing sports coaching teams.
Built with Kotlin and Firebase as a portfolio project.

---

## About

CoachPro helps coaches manage their players, practice sessions,
attendance, and performance stats — all in one place.

Built by a real Basketball Coach at Vision International School, Vadodara.

---

## Features

- Login & Register with Firebase Authentication
- Dashboard with real-time stats
- Players Module — Add, View, Edit, Delete
- Sessions Module — Schedule & manage practice sessions
- Attendance Module — Mark Present / Absent per session
- Performance Module — Track Points, Assists, Rebounds, Effort & Defense
- Profile — Coach info, team stats & logout

---

## Tech Stack

- Language     : Kotlin
- UI           : XML Layouts + ViewBinding
- Navigation   : Navigation Component + Bottom Navigation
- Database     : Firebase Cloud Firestore
- Auth         : Firebase Authentication
- Design       : Material Design — Dark Theme + Orange Accent
- Min SDK      : API 24 (Android 7.0+)
- IDE          : Android Studio Otter 2025.2.1

